        dc:description           "FIGURES 280–288. Primary type specimens and labels of New Zealand Zopheridae: Synchitini. 280–281) Holotype, Pristoderus punctatus (Broun, 1886; as Ulonotus); labels; 282–284) Lectotype, Pristoderus reitteri (Sharp, 1882; as Acosmetus); card-mount; labels; 285–287) Lectotype, Pristoderus rudis (Sharp, 1877; as Enarsus); labels; 288) Lectotype, Pristoderus rufescens (Broun, 1886; as Ulonotus)." ;
